OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780942271
OL,3,CAssociate of Manchester Synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker admits to terror charges
OL,6,FAn Islamic extremist has admitted
OL,7,Fplanning a terror attack on the UK's
OL,8,FDefence Academy with the man who went
OL,9,Fon to kill two men during a knife
OL,10,Frampage at a Manchester synagogue.
OL,12,FMohammad Bashir, 31, pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fthe preparation of terrorist acts at
OL,14,Fthe Old Bailey on Friday 5 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
