PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780942271
OL,3,CAssociate of Manchester Synagogue
OL,4,Cattacker admits to terror charges
OL,6,FShe ordered a pre-sentence report,
OL,7,Ftelling bearded Bashir, of Shaftsbury
OL,8,FRoad, Manchester, he had pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to a "very serious charge".
OL,11,FBashir entered his guilty plea on
OL,12,FFriday, a month before his scheduled
OL,13,Ftrial from 6 July in Manchester.
OL,15,FHe was further remanded into custody.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
